title: Carrvale United F.C.
text:
Carrvale United F.C. was an <a href="England">English</a> <a href="association%20football">football</a> club.
History.
The club was a member of the <a href="Midland%20League%20%281889%29">Midland League</a> during the late 1970s, finishing 4th in 1978, and also competed in the <a href="FA%20Vase">FA Vase</a> on two occasions.
